to do this one for me.

41:52.166 --> 41:55.041
As a final courtesy.

41:59.291 --> 42:02.250
Sure, sir.

42:02.250 --> 42:04.625
Come by my chambers
Friday morning.

42:04.625 --> 42:06.208
