by then.

42:06.208 --> 42:07.583
And thank y--

42:07.583 --> 42:09.208
You're welcome, Chaz.

42:18.458 --> 42:20.416
Give me your phone.

42:22.208 --> 42:25.041
We need our I.T. staff back
and your focus.

42:25.041 --> 42:27.875
