the Internet pointlessly.

42:27.875 --> 42:29.708
I'm logging you on to Raya.

42:29.708 --> 42:32.208
-How?
-I'm a member, so I vouch.

42:32.208 --> 42:34.708
You need two reccos.
I got Michael Che to second you.

42:34.708 --> 42:37.416
Can't have you distracting
our staff with this bullshit.

42:37.416 --> 42:39.458
-You're a member?
