that you're a signer on.

43:57.750 --> 43:59.916
Right around, uh,

43:59.916 --> 44:02.666
well, hell, right on

44:02.666 --> 44:06.250
the day that you suspended
your investigation into him.

44:06.250 --> 44:09.666
$5 million.

44:09.666 --> 44:12.583
Now,

44:12.583 --> 44:15.208
