44:15.208 --> 44:18.541
but, dang,
if it doesn't look like one

44:18.541 --> 44:20.291
and smell like one.

44:20.291 --> 44:22.916
And if I
put my tongue on it,

44:22.916 --> 44:25.916
I bet it tastes like one,
