45:55.208 --> 45:58.208
some things that I cannot
imagine keeping to myself.

45:58.208 --> 46:01.250
For instance,
if I had suddenly received

46:01.250 --> 46:04.000
a $5 million
lump-sum payment

46:04.000 --> 46:06.666
the same day that my husband
dropped an investigation

46:06.666 --> 46:08.791
on the man making that payment,

46:08.791 --> 46:12.083
