your reputation in question.

46:33.916 --> 46:35.666
Not just my reputation.

46:35.666 --> 46:38.833
My job.

46:38.833 --> 46:40.291
Perhaps my freedom.

46:40.291 --> 46:41.916
Perhaps yours.

46:41.916 --> 46:44.125
