46:44.125 --> 46:46.666
I am just beginning to remember
what that feels like.

46:46.666 --> 46:48.041
And I'm not gonna
let you ruin

46:48.041 --> 46:50.416
one of the first free nights
I've had in years.

46:50.416 --> 46:54.041
