47:32.041 --> 47:34.875
I watched people running toward
the betting window

47:34.875 --> 47:38.208
with high hopes.

47:38.208 --> 47:40.166
No plan.

47:40.166 --> 47:42.416
Then I'd watch them
walk away from the track

47:42.416 --> 47:46.166
