but first I figured out

47:53.500 --> 47:56.125
where the sharp action was,

47:56.125 --> 47:59.500
where the guys who
had a plan were,

47:59.500 --> 48:01.291
guys who grinded,

48:01.291 --> 48:03.208
take the guesswork
out of it.

48:03.208 --> 48:05.041
They knew which drivers
had been rested.

48:05.041 --> 48:07.041
They knew
which horses were ready.

48:07.041 --> 48:10.333
And they also knew which ones
were on last legs.

48:10.333 --> 48:13.083
How'd you meet those guys?

48:13.083 --> 48:15.166
I didn't at first.

48:15.166 --> 48:17.000
But I figured out

48:17.000 --> 48:21.083
that they always bet late
and they bet heavy.

48:24.125 --> 48:27.000
So I started watching that

48:27.000 --> 48:30.125
instead of that.

48:30.125 --> 48:33.708
The numbers told the story.
They always do.

48:33.708 --> 48:36.208
I started making bets
of my own.

48:36.208 --> 48:38.333
You know,
the right ones.

48:38.333 --> 48:40.666
And once I understood
what had happened,

48:40.666 --> 48:44.041
I watched the track
to see how it happened.

48:47.083 --> 48:49.125
Strange time
for a workout.

48:49.125 --> 48:51.750
Yeah, he comes here
most days of the week.

48:51.750 --> 48:54.208
Likes to run his new prospects
out under the lights,

48:54.208 --> 48:57.708
get them used to it.

49:00.791 --> 49:03.750
He's a good driver.

49:03.750 --> 49:05.458
But his father --

49:05.458 --> 49:07.541
His father was
the best there was.

49:07.541 --> 49:10.083
True master.
Hall of Fame.

49:10.083 --> 49:11.750
