49:29.125 --> 49:33.208
I could open myself up
to a big loss

49:33.208 --> 49:36.208
if I made a move and miss.

49:38.333 --> 49:40.083
When I used to come down here,

49:40.083 --> 49:43.041
I had nothing,
so I-I just figured it out.

49:43.041 --> 49:45.333
That you did.

49:47.333 --> 49:49.458
I need Rhoades gone.

49:49.458 --> 49:52.500
Or this will never be over.

49:52.500 --> 49:55.541
My suit alone,

49:55.541 --> 49:59.208
it's like me firing a pea
shooter against a Panzer tank

49:59.208 --> 50:02.625
when what we need
