50:02.625 --> 50:05.250
But I know how we can
get ourselves a Howie.

50:08.208 --> 50:11.125
We find everybody
that he fucked,

50:11.125 --> 50:13.958
who went away aggrieved,

50:13.958 --> 50:17.375
people with real grounds,

50:17.375 --> 50:19.208
and we buy up their claims.

50:19.208 --> 50:21.875
Ah.

50:21.875 --> 50:24.291
Aggregate the lawsuits.

50:24.291 --> 50:26.125
Where one is weak,
many are strong.

50:26.125 --> 50:29.208
