50:34.000 --> 50:36.000
Not possible to.

50:36.000 --> 50:39.041
The stories won't be about you
anymore. They'll be about him.

50:39.041 --> 50:42.708
And the world of shit
that he is in.

50:44.833 --> 50:47.041
You know what
you have to do?

50:51.458 --> 50:54.083
I know what I have to do.

50:59.250 --> 51:03.125
This guy doesn't really come out
here a few times a week.

51:03.125 --> 51:04.250
No.

51:04.250 --> 51:05.750
